OL,7,FA man from Cheshire has been convicted
OL,8,Fof unlawfully obtaining people's
OL,9,Fpersonal information from vehicle
OL,10,Frepair garages to generate potential
OL,11,Fleads for personal injury claims.
OL,13,FA jury at Bolton Crown Court found
OL,14,FCraig Cornick, 40, of Prestbury,
OL,15,Fguilty of conspiracy to unlawfully
OL,16,Fobtain personal data contrary to the
OL,17,FData Protection Act.
