OL,7,FSeven other men from Cheshire and
OL,8,FGreater Manchester had previously
OL,9,Fpleaded guilty to conspiracy to
OL,10,Funlawfully obtain personal data.
OL,12,FThe Information Commissioner's Office
OL,13,F(ICO) has welcomed the verdict at the
OL,14,Fend of a 10 week trial. During its
OL,15,Finvestigation the the ICO seized the
OL,16,Fwidest body of evidence it has ever
OL,17,Fseen, demonstrating the misuse of
OL,18,Fpeople's personal details to make
OL,19,Fnuisance calls to try and persuade
OL,20,Fpeople to make personal injury claims.
