OL,7,FEarlier in the month, the jury
OL,8,Freturned a not guilty verdict for
OL,9,FCornick and Thomas Daly, 35, of
OL,10,FMacclesfield, for a charge of
OL,11,Fconspiracy to access computer systems
OL,12,Fwithout authority contrary to the
OL,13,FComputer Misuse Act.
OL,15,FDaly had previously pleaded guilty to
OL,16,Ftwo counts of conspiracy to unlawfully
OL,17,Fobtain personal data.
OL,19,FSix other men had all previously
OL,20,Fpleaded guilty to the offences listed
OL,21,Fbelow:
