OL,7,FThe defendants were found to have
OL,8,Fconspired together between 2014 and
OL,9,F2017, where they accessed and obtained
OL,10,Fpersonal data of approximately one
OL,11,Fmillion people from vehicle repair
OL,12,Fgarages without their consent.
