OL,7,FThis data was then sold onto claims
OL,8,Fmanagement firms hoping to generate
OL,9,Fpotential leads for personal injury
OL,10,Fclaims. The ICO has an ongoing second
OL,11,Fphase of its investigation and
OL,12,Fanticipates further prosecutions of
OL,13,Fpeople embedded into insurance
OL,14,Fcompanies and claims management
OL,15,Fcompanies with the sole aim of
OL,16,Fstealing personal data.
