OL,7,FAfter identifying the people involved,
OL,8,Fthe ICO's investigations team
OL,9,Fconducted nine warrants in the
OL,10,FManchester and Macclesfield areas. The
OL,11,Fdevices seized under search warrant
OL,12,Fcontained 241,000 emails, 4.5 million
OL,13,Fdocuments, 144,000 spreadsheets, 1.5
OL,14,Fmillion images and 83,000 multimedia
OL,15,Ffiles.
