OL,4,Cunlawfully obtaining personal data
OL,5,Cfrom garages
OL,7,FICO's Head of Investigations, Andy
OL,8,FCurry, said: "Most of us have had
OL,9,Fnuisance calls asking if we've been in
OL,10,Fa crash. At best they're annoying but
OL,11,Fat worst they cause real upset and
OL,12,Ffear, especially to vulnerable people,
OL,13,Fand have a real impact on the
OL,14,Fbusinesses affected.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
