OL,5,Cfrom garages
OL,7,F"This case uncovered a vast, murky
OL,8,Fcriminal network where crash details
OL,9,Fwere stolen from garages across
OL,10,FEngland, Scotland and Wales and traded
OL,11,Fto fuel distressing predatory calls.
OL,12,FThis has been an enormous and complex
OL,13,Fcase which has seen ICO staff use both
OL,14,Ftechnical expertise and investigative
OL,15,Fskills to work tirelessly to track
OL,16,Fdown those responsible and hold them
OL,17,Faccountable on behalf of the public."
